  _description: "ActionFit UPM \uD328\uD0A4\uC9C0 \uCE74\uD0C8\uB85C\uADF8\uB97C
    \uBCF4\uACE0 Git URL \uAE30\uBC18 \uC124\uCE58\uC640 \uBC84\uC804 \uC801\uC6A9\uC744
    \uB3C4\uC640\uC8FC\uB294 Unity \uC5D0\uB514\uD130 \uD234."
  _releaseNote: '## 1.1.27

    - Package Manager menu was reorganized to `Tools
    > ActionFit > Package Manager > Package Manager`, and operational tools moved
    to `Manager Console`. The main install/update window now keeps only the buttons
    needed for package management.

    - `Manager Console` now groups create, repo,
    publish, README, catalog, manifest, and settings actions in a separate window,
    reducing toolbar clutter in daily package install flows.

    - The new `Updates`
    panel collects installed packages whose catalog latest version differs from the
    current version. Downloaded packages can be updated individually, by selection,
    or all at once.

    - Update history viewing was added. `History` shows all
    catalog changelogs newest to oldest, while `Changes` shows only the changelogs
    between the installed version and the selected target version.

    - Embedded
    packages still appear in update checks, but Git UPM update actions remain disabled
    until the embedded package folder is removed.

    - README and package metadata
    Korean text were restored from mojibake and updated for the new menu paths and
    update management flow.'
  _dependenciesOverride: 
